on, which I summarized in the aforementioned What Clayton Christensen Got W=
rong ( https://stratechery.com/2013/clayton-christensen-got-wrong/?access_t=
oken=3DeyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6InN0cmF0ZWNoZXJ5LnBhc3Nwb3J0Lm9ubGluZSIs=
